      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a mistake though. it's everything. i look at them and i just feel like a curse. like i'm just a shadow hanging over their lives. i can't help but think that if i wasn't here, they wouldn't have to deal with my baggage or see me struggle like this. they could actually be happy.",
